0:00:04.400,0:00:09.580
Uchapupu hwangu hunotanga sezvizvi: Chokutanga pane zvose, Good Morning, Chechi!

0:00:09.580,0:00:12.420
Good Morning, Chechi!

0:00:12.420,0:00:20.440
Muna 2011, ndakanga ndine dumbu rakakura se dhiramu. Ndaifunga kuti rakanga risiri pamuviri; izvo zvaiva zvechokwadi.

0:00:20.440,0:00:32.100
Pandakaenda kuchipatara, ivo vakati ndakanga ndine bundu muchibereko uye ndaifanirwa kuitwa oparesheni.

0:00:32.100,0:00:36.740
Zvadaro, ndakaenda kune shamwari yangu. Akati kwandiri, "Usaitwe, oparesheni enda ku SCOAN".

0:00:36.740,0:00:42.440
Saka, ndakauya ku SCOAN. Ini chaizvoizvo ndaifanira kuenda kungungano rekunze kwe chechi

0:00:42.440,0:00:47.860
Ndakanyengeterera ikoko uye ndakagamuchirawo Morning Water.

0:00:47.860,0:00:55.540
Ipapo ndakadzokera kumusha. Ndakapfapfaidza Morning Water pandiri uye ndikanwa.

0:00:55.540,0:01:02.500
Muna 2012, ndakaenda kunotariswa kuchipatara uye vakaramba vachindiudza kuti ndaifanira kunovhiyiwa. Ndakati, "Kwete".

0:01:02.500,0:01:07.220
Muna 2013, handina kumboita hanya nekuenda kuchipatara. Ndakanga ndichinyengetera nekunyengetera

0:01:07.220,0:01:12.440
uye zvose, zvandakashamisika nazvo, zvakangonyangarika.

0:01:12.440,0:01:19.420
Izvi ndizvo zvamuri kundiona ndiri zvino.

0:01:19.420,0:01:21.520
Tinonyatsoda kunzwisisa hupupuriro hwako.

0:01:21.520,0:01:27.500
Imi mati, mushure mekunge masvika pano ... Chokutanga pane zvose, chii chakakuitai kuti muuye pano

0:01:27.500,0:01:34.140
